## User Stories

### Fan Stories
- U-020: Subscribe to creator for content access
- U-021: Purchase PPV to unlock specific posts
- U-022: Tip creators to show appreciation
- U-023: Manage subscriptions (cancel, renew)
- U-024: Add funds to wallet
- U-025: View transaction history
- U-026: Purchase subscription bundles for savings

### Creator Stories
- C-020: Receive subscription payments
- C-021: Receive PPV payments
- C-022: Receive tips
- C-026: Weekly payouts to bank account

---

## Technical Requirements

### Payment Flow

```
User Action → Square Checkout → Payment Success → 
  → Update DB (subscription/ppv_purchase/transaction)
  → Grant Access
  → Send Notification
```

### Subscription Plans

| Plan | Duration | Discount |
|------|----------|----------|
| Monthly | 1 month | 0% |
| 3-Month | 3 months | 10% (creator-set) |
| 6-Month | 6 months | 20% (creator-set) |
| 12-Month | 12 months | 30% (creator-set) |

### Revenue Split

| Party | Percentage |
|-------|------------|
| Creator | 85% |
| Platform | 15% |

