## API Endpoints (21 Total)

### Subscriptions (5)
- POST `/api/subscriptions/[creatorId]` - Subscribe
- GET `/api/subscriptions` - List subscriptions
- PATCH `/api/subscriptions/[id]` - Update/cancel
- POST `/api/subscriptions/[id]/renew` - Renew
- GET `/api/creator/subscribers` - List subscribers

### Payments (3)
- POST `/api/payments/checkout` - Create checkout
- GET/POST/DELETE `/api/payments/cards` - Saved cards
- POST `/api/webhooks/square/payments` - Webhook

### Wallet (3)
- GET `/api/wallet` - Get balance
- POST `/api/wallet/topup` - Add funds
- GET `/api/wallet/transactions` - History

### PPV (2)
- POST `/api/ppv/[postId]/purchase` - Purchase
- GET `/api/ppv/purchases` - User purchases

### Tips (2)
- POST `/api/tips` - Send tip
- GET `/api/tips/received` - Creator tips

### Payouts (2)
- GET `/api/creator/payouts` - Payout history
- GET/PATCH `/api/creator/payouts/settings` - Settings

### Transactions (2)
- GET `/api/transactions` - User history
- GET `/api/creator/transactions` - Creator earnings
- GET `/api/transactions/export` - CSV export

